  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together lime juice, olive oil, garlic, and Uruguayan oregano.",
    "Add beef strips, red onion, and red bell pepper to the bowl. Toss to coat with marinade.",
    "Thread beef and vegetables onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until beef reaches 135°F for medium-rare.",
    "Transfer skewers to a plate and let rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
